name: PIM_Beta_Blockers
title: PIM_Beta_Blockers
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Comprehensive set of RxNorm codes for medications that contain beta blockers. The intended use is to identify beta blocker allergies. If a patient has an allergy associated with any of these RxCUIs, we will consider them to be allergic to beta blockers),(Data Element Scope: DRUG_CLASS_MEMBERS: PHARMACOLOGIC),(Inclusion Criteria: Any RxCUI associated with a beta blocker as an ingredient),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
